{"tid":1119661,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"本地 少女 終身美麗","createTime":"2019-04-22T05:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T06:58:12.000Z","uid":64126,"like":15,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"023b2c06f0bb93ead1bd6733ae89012d13ebb3c1","tid":1119661,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:45:49.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打復活節快樂！好耐沒見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次想黎個小小既sharing <br />\n<br />\n現代人生活忙碌 節奏急速 總愛貪新忘舊 <br />\n往往忽略左好多背後為你默默耕耘既人 <br />\n有時細心留意 可能你會發現得更多<br />\n好好珍惜眼前人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n終身美麗 - 鄭秀文<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/mysecretguarden/maqz0jwicq3b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fmysecretguarden%2Fmaqz0jwicq3b&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6rM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=c82b4b04\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/mysecretguarden/maqz0jwicq3b</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第21星期<br />\n第9首歌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f389329a465dd4dc5b20341e2f7a4fa36ddd7cc7","tid":1119661,"uid":64126,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"鄭秀文 - 終身美麗<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：陳輝陽<br />\n<br />\n塔尖仍舊記得 這擁抱極美好<br />\n愛有千斤重 重過無涯的鐵路<br />\n你那手指再笨拙再粗 肌膚也被你修補<br />\n從前那一位 永未能做到<br />\n<br />\n是你去喚醒我 努力才能被愛慕<br />\n但回頭目睹你 為我好自己不好<br />\n我這幸運兒合著眼睛 只得你沉重身影<br />\n如果這記憶非愛情 連天都不會太高興<br />\n<br />\n莫非可終生美麗 才值得勾勾手指發誓<br />\n對你不止感激敬禮 當你知己才是虛偽<br />\n莫非多一分秀麗 才值得分享我的一切<br />\n給我自信 給我地位 這叫幸福 不怕流逝<br />\n任他們多漂亮 未及你矜貴"},{"pid":"9a0269cabee8e22173bef6a0984efc2cb4dd4e62","tid":1119661,"uid":100299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"31e9afed6c2600884a768f75462bfd5e6a9e347c","tid":1119661,"uid":152262,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"終於等到<img src=\"/assets/